case.name: Tick's Arm Falls Off 1
case.description: Oh dear, what a predicament, as Tick was prepared to strip, one of his faulty robot arms fall off!

case.name: Tick's Arm Falls Off 2
case.description: Unfortunately, his other arm also falls off as well. He seems to be displeased.

case.name: Tick's Head Detaches
case.description: As a last resort, his head detaches itself from his body, leaving him with only his bouncing head.

case.name: Tick Explodes and Disappears
case.description: TICK FUCKING DIES. (Don't worry, the explosion is harmless...but it may cause brief blindless.)
